data.enText: the state of being a member of a group, a club, an organization, etc.

data.chText: 谁有资格申请加入这个协会？
data.enText: Who is eligible to apply for membership of the association?

data.chText: （统称）会员，成员；会员人数；成员数

data.hoverText: 可与单数或复数动词连用的可数名词

data.enText: the members, or the number of members, of a group, a club, an organization, etc.
The membership has/have not yet voted.

data.chText: 俱乐部的会员人数超过了500名。
data.enText: The club has a membership of more than 500.

simple_means.memory_skill: member 成员，会员 + ship 身份，职位，资格 → 会员资格；会员身份

tr: the body of members of an organization or group
example: they found dissension in their own ranks
he joined the ranks of the unemployed

tr: the state of being a member

value.def: Membership of an organization is the state of being a member of it.

example.ex: The country has also been granted membership of the World Trade Organisation...
example.tran: 这个国家也被准予加入世界贸易组织。

example.ex: He sent me a membership form...
example.tran: 他寄给我一份入会登记表。

example.ex: Membership in her church youth group helped develop her political ideas.
example.tran: 加入教会青年团契促使她形成了自己的政治观点。

value.def: The membership of an organization is the people who belong to it, or the number of people who belong to it.

example.ex: The European Builders Confederation has a membership of over 350,000 building companies.
example.tran: 欧洲建筑商联合会拥有逾35万家建筑公司会员。

value.tran: 全体会员(或成员);全体会员(或成员)人数

trans: 准会员资格；非正式会员资格
